      "span_text": "Differences in response to the active substance stem from patient-related factors (genetic factors, body weight, smoking, liver function, kidney function, physical activity or feeding status) and from the properties of the drug (physicochemical properties of the active substance and interactions with other substances can lead to adverse effects) [CITATION_2] ."
